We looked at the characteristics of the out of work population from many angles [all the dimensions of the cluster analysis]. We used these data to identify discrete groupings of people within each jurisdication and then to categorize each grouping into broad groups. These groups provide a meaningful entry point to the discussion of workforce challenges and priorities for each jurisdiction in the dataset.
